Deprecated. As of release 2.5, replaced by de.systemagmbh.tools.io.mail.CSysSMTPSender

public class CSysMailWriterStream
extends PrintStream

This is a Helper-class emulating a PrintStream by redirecting output to the mailhost and inheriting the println() functionality you know and overwriting the underlying methods write(...). This class can only be used together with a class implementing ISysMail.
